----[ Purpose

	Adds settings to ensure password complexity requirements are met

----[ Features

	Minimum Password Length
	Require Numerical Characters
	Require Mixed Case
	Require Special Characters
	Option to force complexity upon old passwords (upon login)
	Expire Passwords after X days
	Disabling Inactive Accounts after X days
	Password History
	Account Locking after X failed attempts
	Auto Unlocked after X minutes

----[ Installation

	Plugin is Plugin Architecture 2.0 only compatible
	To install, place it in your plugin directory in a folder called "secpass"
	Then login to Cacti, goto Plugin Management and click "Install" next to the plugin's name

	You can then edit the text under Settings >> "Authenication" tab >> Complexity Requirements
    
